3	// This file implements ListModels for the FizeauService service.
4	// It lives in the root package to avoid import cycles; provider and catalog
5	// data is injected via ServiceConfig (defined in service.go).
6	//
7	// Provider-backed models are assembled from the unified model snapshot used by
8	// the CLI model inventory path. Codex and Claude expose a separate
9	// harness-native surface backed by PTY/CLI evidence.
10	
